title: The World's Assault Rifles by Gary Paul Johnston (.epub)
description:
The World's Assault Rifles by Gary Paul Johnston, Thomas B. Nelson 

Requirements: .ePUB reader, 34,9 MB

Genre: Non-Fiction > General

Overview: 

With technical and design data starting from the early 1900's to what is on the drawing boards for tomorrow, this encyclopedic volume covers every facet of the assault rifle - all within a lively and detailed historical perspective that brings the subject into three-dimensional focus - to create the best volume ever published on the topic. 70 chapters comprising more than 1,200 thoroughly indexed pages with nearly 2,000 illustrations
